name: Toby Dirtymartini
bio:
Have a Birthday, Corporate event, Bachelorette party, networking or social event? 
Dirty Martini offers three different sections designed to accommodate and entertain all special gatherings.  With privacy arrangements and VIP ambiance, Dirty Martini will exclusively cater to your party needs and desires.  With menu options and pre-designed packages, Dirty Martini will provide your party with more than just the basics but an eclectic experience.  Book your party today!
